&lt;p style="line-height: normal; margin: 0in 0in 0pt;" class="MsoNormal"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: 'Times New Roman','serif'; color: black; font-size: 9.5pt;" lang="TR"&gt;Bu belge, t&amp;uuml;m adımları aşağıda daha ayrıntılı bir şekilde i&amp;ccedil;ermektedir.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Jul 2011 23:28:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">http://localhost:80/preparing-VPS-templates/overview-tr-TR</guid></item><item><title>Hyper-V Sunucuyu Yönetme</title><link>http://localhost:80/preparing-VPS-templates/managing-hyper-v-server-tr-TR</link><description>&lt;p style="line-height: normal; margin-bottom: 0pt;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: 'Arial','sans-serif'; font-size: 9.5pt;" lang="TR"&gt;&lt;a href="http://www.websitepanel.net/documentation"&gt;&lt;span style="color: #000000;" color="#000000"&gt;Belgeler&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &amp;gt; &lt;a href="http://www.websitepanel.net/preparing-VPS-templates/index"&gt;&lt;span style="color: #000000;" color="#000000"&gt;VPS Şablonları Hazırlama&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h1 style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: 'Arial','sans-serif'; font-size: 17pt;" lang="TR"&gt;Hyper-V Sunucuyu Y&amp;ouml;netme&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p style="line-height: normal; margin-bottom: 0pt;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: 'Arial','sans-serif'; font-size: 9.5pt;" lang="TR"&gt;Hyper-V rol&amp;uuml; kurulu tam Windows Server 2008 &amp;uuml;zerinde VHD ve sanal bilgisayar ile &amp;ccedil;alışmak daha uygundur. &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="line-height: normal; margin-bottom: 0pt;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: 'Arial','sans-serif'; font-size: 9.5pt;" lang="TR"&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="line-height: normal; margin-bottom: 0pt;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: 'Arial','sans-serif'; font-size: 9.5pt;" lang="TR"&gt;Ancak uzak Hyper-V Server 2008 veya Windows Server 2008 Sunucu &amp;Ccedil;ekirdeği kurulu ise &amp;ldquo;Windows Vista i&amp;ccedil;in Hyper-V Uzaktan Y&amp;ouml;netim G&amp;uuml;ncellemesini (KB952627)&amp;rdquo; kullanabilirsiniz: &lt;a href="http://www.microsoft.com/downloads/details.aspx?FamilyID=BF909242-2125-4D06-A968-C8A3D75FF2AA&amp;amp;displaylang=en"&gt;&lt;span style="color: #000000;" color="#000000"&gt;http://www.microsoft.com/downloads/details.aspx?FamilyID=BF909242-2125-4D06-A968-C8A3D75FF2AA&amp;amp;displaylang=en&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="line-height: normal; margin-bottom: 0pt;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: 'Arial','sans-serif'; font-size: 9.5pt;" lang="TR"&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="line-height: normal; margin-bottom: 0pt;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: 'Arial','sans-serif'; font-size: 9.5pt;" lang="TR"&gt;64-bit Vista i&amp;ccedil;in:&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="line-height: normal; margin-bottom: 0pt;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: 'Arial','sans-serif'; font-size: 9.5pt;" lang="TR"&gt;&lt;a href="http://www.microsoft.com/downloads/details.aspx?familyid=88208468-0AD6-47DE-8580-085CBA42C0C2&amp;amp;displaylang=en"&gt;&lt;span style="color: #000000;" color="#000000"&gt;http://www.microsoft.com/downloads/details.aspx?familyid=88208468-0AD6-47DE-8580-085CBA42C0C2&amp;amp;displaylang=en&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="line-height: normal; margin-bottom: 0pt;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: 'Arial','sans-serif'; font-size: 9.5pt;" lang="TR"&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="line-height: normal; margin-bottom: 0pt;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: 'Arial','sans-serif'; font-size: 9.5pt;" lang="TR"&gt;Bu g&amp;uuml;ncelleme ile ilgili &amp;ouml;nemli notlar: &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="line-height: normal; margin-bottom: 0pt;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: 'Arial','sans-serif'; font-size: 9.5pt;" lang="TR"&gt;1. Windows Vista Home Basic veya Premium s&amp;uuml;r&amp;uuml;mlerinde &amp;ccedil;alışmaz. &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="line-height: normal; margin-bottom: 0pt;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: 'Arial','sans-serif'; font-size: 9.5pt;" lang="TR"&gt;2. &amp;ldquo;Y&amp;ouml;netim Ara&amp;ccedil;ları&amp;rdquo; men&amp;uuml; &amp;ouml;ğesi etkinleştirilmelidir:&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="line-height: normal; margin-bottom: 0pt;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: 'Arial','sans-serif'; font-size: 9.5pt;" lang="TR"&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="line-height: normal; margin-bottom: 0pt;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: 'Arial','sans-serif'; font-size: 9.5pt;" lang="TR"&gt;&amp;ldquo;Y&amp;ouml;netim Ara&amp;ccedil;ları&amp;rdquo; men&amp;uuml;s&amp;uuml;n&amp;uuml; etkinleştirmek i&amp;ccedil;in G&amp;ouml;rev &amp;Ccedil;ubuğunu sağ tıklatın -&amp;gt; &amp;ldquo;&amp;Ouml;zellikler&amp;rdquo; men&amp;uuml; &amp;ouml;ğesi -&amp;gt; &amp;ldquo;Başlat men&amp;uuml;s&amp;uuml;&amp;rdquo; sekmesi -&amp;gt; &amp;ldquo;&amp;Ouml;zelleştir...&amp;rdquo; d&amp;uuml;ğmesini tıklatın.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="line-height: normal; margin-bottom: 0pt;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: 'Arial','sans-serif'; font-size: 9.5pt;" lang="TR"&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="line-height: normal; margin-bottom: 0pt;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: 'Arial','sans-serif'; font-size: 9.5pt;" lang="TR"&gt;Tam Windows Server 2008 uzaktan y&amp;ouml;netim i&amp;ccedil;in &amp;ldquo;Windows Vista i&amp;ccedil;in Microsoft Uzak Sunucu Y&amp;ouml;netim Ara&amp;ccedil;larını (KB941314)&amp;rdquo; kullanabilirsiniz: &lt;a href="http://www.microsoft.com/downloads/details.aspx?FamilyID=9ff6e897-23ce-4a36-b7fc-d52065de9960&amp;amp;displaylang=en"&gt;&lt;span style="color: #000000;" color="#000000"&gt;http://www.microsoft.com/downloads/details.aspx?FamilyID=9ff6e897-23ce-4a36-b7fc-d52065de9960&amp;amp;displaylang=en&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="line-height: normal; margin-bottom: 0pt;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: 'Arial','sans-serif'; font-size: 9.5pt;" lang="TR"&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="line-height: normal; margin-bottom: 0pt;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: 'Arial','sans-serif'; font-size: 9.5pt;" lang="TR"&gt;64-bit Vista i&amp;ccedil;in:&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="line-height: normal; margin-bottom: 0pt;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: 'Arial','sans-serif'; font-size: 9.5pt;" lang="TR"&gt;&lt;a href="http://www.microsoft.com/downloads/details.aspx?familyid=D647A60B-63FD-4AC5-9243-BD3C497D2BC5&amp;amp;displaylang=en"&gt;&lt;span style="color: #000000;" color="#000000"&gt;http://www.microsoft.com/downloads/details.aspx?familyid=D647A60B-63FD-4AC5-9243-BD3C497D2BC5&amp;amp;displaylang=en&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="line-height: normal; margin-bottom: 0pt;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: 'Arial','sans-serif'; font-size: 9.5pt;" lang="TR"&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="line-height: normal; margin-bottom: 0pt;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: 'Arial','sans-serif'; font-size: 9.5pt;" lang="TR"&gt;&amp;Ouml;nemli notlar: &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="line-height: normal; margin-bottom: 0pt;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: 'Arial','sans-serif'; font-size: 9.5pt;" lang="TR"&gt;1. Windows Vista Business s&amp;uuml;r&amp;uuml;m&amp;uuml; veya daha yukarısı gereklidir &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="line-height: normal; margin-bottom: 0pt;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: 'Arial','sans-serif'; font-size: 9.5pt;" lang="TR"&gt;2. Service Pack 1 kurulu olmalıdır. &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="line-height: normal; margin-bottom: 0pt;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: 'Arial','sans-serif'; font-size: 9.5pt;" lang="TR"&gt;T&amp;uuml;m &amp;ouml;rneklerimizde Hyper-V rol&amp;uuml;n&amp;uuml;n kurulu olduğu tam Windows kurulumu kullanılacaktır.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;pre style="line-height: normal; margin: 0in 0in 0pt; background: white;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: Consolas;" lang="TR"&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: small;" size="3"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Jul 2011 23:28:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">http://localhost:80/preparing-VPS-templates/managing-hyper-v-server-tr-TR</guid></item><item><title>Ana Sanal Bilgisayar Oluşturma</title><link>http://localhost:80/preparing-VPS-templates/creating-master-virtual-machine-tr-TR</link><description>&lt;p style="line-height: normal; margin: 0in 0in 0pt;" class="MsoNormal"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: 'Times New Roman','serif'; color: black; font-size: 9.5pt;" lang="TR"&gt;&lt;a href="http://www.websitepanel.net/documentation"&gt;&lt;span style="color: black; text-decoration: none; text-underline: none;"&gt;Belgeler&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &amp;gt; &lt;a href="http://www.websitepanel.net/preparing-VPS-templates/index"&gt;&lt;span style="color: black; text-decoration: none; text-underline: none;"&gt;VPS Şablonları Hazırlama&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="line-height: normal; margin: 0in 0in 0pt; mso-outline-level: 1;" class="MsoNormal"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: 'Times New Roman','serif'; color: black; font-size: 17pt; mso-font-kerning: 18.0pt;" lang="TR"&gt;Ana Sanal Bilgisayar Oluşturma&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="line-height: normal; margin: 0in 0in 0pt;" class="MsoNormal"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: 'Times New Roman','serif'; color: black; font-size: 9.5pt;" lang="TR"&gt;Şablon VHD ile birlikte kullanılacak bir &amp;ldquo;ana&amp;rdquo; sanal bilgisayar oluşturmanız gereklidir. &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="line-height: normal; margin: 0in 0in 0pt;" class="MsoNormal"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: 'Times New Roman','serif'; color: black; font-size: 9.5pt;" lang="TR"&gt;Ana sanal bilgisayara misafir OS kurmak i&amp;ccedil;in, bir .ISO dosyası veya işletim sistemi dağıtılabilir olan bir fiziksel DVD gereklidir. DVD ISO dosyalarını MSDN aboneliklerinden y&amp;uuml;kleyebilirsiniz. &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="line-height: normal; margin: 0in 0in 0pt;" class="MsoNormal"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: 'Times New Roman','serif'; color: black; font-size: 9.5pt;" lang="TR"&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="line-height: normal; margin: 0in 0in 0pt;" class="MsoNormal"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: 'Times New Roman','serif'; color: black; font-size: 9.5pt;" lang="TR"&gt;&amp;ldquo;Hyper-V Y&amp;ouml;neticisi&amp;rdquo; uygulamasını a&amp;ccedil;ın ve sanal bilgisayar oluşturma sihirbazını başlatmak i&amp;ccedil;in işlem men&amp;uuml;s&amp;uuml;nden &amp;ldquo;Yeni -&amp;gt; Sanal Bilgisayar...&amp;rdquo; &amp;ouml;ğesini se&amp;ccedil;in. &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="line-height: normal; margin: 0in 0in 0pt;" class="MsoNormal"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: 'Times New Roman','serif'; color: black; font-size: 9.5pt;" lang="TR"&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="line-height: normal; text-indent: -0.25in; margin: 0in 0in 0pt 0.25in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;" class="MsoNormal"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: Symbol; color: black; font-size: 9.5pt; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;" lang="TR"&gt;&lt;span style="mso-list: Ignore;"&gt;&amp;middot;&lt;span style="font: 7pt 'Times New Roman';"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: 'Times New Roman','serif'; color: black; font-size: 9.5pt;" lang="TR"&gt;Diğerlerinden ayırt edebilmek i&amp;ccedil;in anlamlı bir VM adı verin;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: 'Times New Roman','serif'; color: black; font-size: 9.5pt;" lang="TR"&gt; &amp;ouml;rneğin &amp;ldquo;Master - Windows 2008 Standard x64&amp;rdquo;. &amp;ldquo;Master - &amp;lt;OS_NAME&amp;gt; &amp;lt;OS_EDITION&amp;gt; &amp;lt;BITNESS&amp;gt; [(INSTALLED_APP_1, INSTALLED_APP_2, ...)] gibi bazı adlandırma kurallarının oluşturulmasını tavsiye ederiz; &amp;ouml;rneğin belirli bir VM'nin Windows Server 2008 Enterprise x64, IIS, SQL Server ve WSP ile kullanılan ana VM olduğunu belirtmek i&amp;ccedil;in şu adı verebilirsiniz: &amp;ldquo;Master &amp;ndash; Windows 2008 Enterprise x64 (IIS, SQL, WSP)&amp;rdquo;.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="line-height: normal; text-indent: -0.25in; margin: 0in 0in 0pt 0.25in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;" class="MsoNormal"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: Symbol; color: black; font-size: 9.5pt; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;" lang="TR"&gt;&lt;span style="mso-list: Ignore;"&gt;&amp;middot;&lt;span style="font: 7pt 'Times New Roman';"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: 'Times New Roman','serif'; color: black; font-size: 9.5pt;" lang="TR"&gt;VM konumunu se&amp;ccedil;in.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: 'Times New Roman','serif'; color: black; font-size: 9.5pt;" lang="TR"&gt; Sanal bilgisayarların ayrı bir sabit disk biriminde depolanması tavsiye edilir. Yedekleme prosed&amp;uuml;r&amp;uuml;n&amp;uuml; kolaylaştıracaktır (VM yedekleme prosed&amp;uuml;r&amp;uuml; ayrı bir WSP VPS &amp;ccedil;&amp;ouml;z&amp;uuml;m kılavuzunda anlatılmaktadır). &amp;Ouml;rneğin, bu durumda sistem birimi C: iken Hyper-V sanal bilgisayarları M: biriminde oluşturulur. Burada da belirli bir klas&amp;ouml;r yapısının oluşturulmasını tavsiye ederiz; &amp;ouml;rneğin m&amp;uuml;şteri sanal bilgisayarları M:\VPS\Customers klas&amp;ouml;r&amp;uuml;nde ve ana VM'ler M:\VPS\Master klas&amp;ouml;r&amp;uuml;nde saklanır.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="line-height: normal; margin: 0in 0in 0pt;" class="MsoNormal"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: 'Times New Roman','serif'; color: black; font-size: 9.5pt;" lang="TR"&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="line-height: normal; text-indent: -0.25in; margin: 0in 0in 0pt 0.25in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;" class="MsoNormal"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: Symbol; color: black; font-size: 9.5pt; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;" lang="TR"&gt;&lt;span style="mso-list: Ignore;"&gt;&amp;middot;&lt;span style="font: 7pt 'Times New Roman';"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: 'Times New Roman','serif'; color: black; font-size: 9.5pt;" lang="TR"&gt;Yeni VM i&amp;ccedil;in Windows Server 2008 &amp;ccedil;alıştırmaya yetecek sanal bellek sağlayın (en az 512MB).&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="line-height: normal; text-indent: -0.25in; margin: 0in 0in 0pt 0.25in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;" class="MsoNormal"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: Symbol; color: black; font-size: 9.5pt; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;" lang="TR"&gt;&lt;span style="mso-list: Ignore;"&gt;&amp;middot;&lt;span style="font: 7pt 'Times New Roman';"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: 'Times New Roman','serif'; color: black; font-size: 9.5pt;" lang="TR"&gt;VM'yi ge&amp;ccedil;erli bir harici ağa bağlayın&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="line-height: normal; text-indent: -0.25in; margin: 0in 0in 0pt 0.25in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;" class="MsoNormal"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: Symbol; color: black; font-size: 9.5pt; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;" lang="TR"&gt;&lt;span style="mso-list: Ignore;"&gt;&amp;middot;&lt;span style="font: 7pt 'Times New Roman';"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: 'Times New Roman','serif'; color: black; font-size: 9.5pt;" lang="TR"&gt;Yalnızca Windows 2008 ve diğer opsiyonel uygulamaları kurmaya yetecek minimum alana sahip bir sanal sabit disk oluşturun. Windows Server 2008 i&amp;ccedil;in en az 10GB gereklidir, bu nedenle uygun sihirbaz adımında boyutu tanımlayarak 15GB boş alan verelim:&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="line-height: normal; text-indent: -0.25in; margin: 0in 0in 0pt 0.25in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;" class="MsoNormal"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: Symbol; color: black; font-size: 9.5pt; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;" lang="TR"&gt;&lt;span style="mso-list: Ignore;"&gt;&amp;middot;&lt;span style="font: 7pt 'Times New Roman';"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: 'Times New Roman','serif'; color: black; font-size: 9.5pt;" lang="TR"&gt;&amp;ldquo;İşletim sistemini kurulum CD/DVD-ROM'undan kur&amp;rdquo; se&amp;ccedil;eneğini se&amp;ccedil;in ve DVD g&amp;ouml;r&amp;uuml;nt&amp;uuml; dosyasını (.ISO) se&amp;ccedil;in veya Hyper-V kurulu bilgisayarda fiziksel DVD s&amp;uuml;r&amp;uuml;c&amp;uuml;y&amp;uuml; kullanın:&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="line-height: normal; text-indent: -0.25in; margin: 0in 0in 0pt 0.25in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;" class="MsoNormal"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: Symbol; color: black; font-size: 9.5pt; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;" lang="TR"&gt;&lt;span style="mso-list: Ignore;"&gt;&amp;middot;&lt;span style="font: 7pt 'Times New Roman';"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: 'Times New Roman','serif'; color: black; font-size: 9.5pt;" lang="TR"&gt;Son sihirbaz adımında &amp;ldquo;Oluşturulduktan sonra sanal bilgisayarı başlat&amp;rdquo; se&amp;ccedil;eneğini se&amp;ccedil;in ve &amp;ldquo;Bitir&amp;rdquo; &amp;ouml;ğesini tıklatın.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Jul 2011 23:27:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">http://localhost:80/preparing-VPS-templates/creating-master-virtual-machine-tr-TR</guid></item><item><title>Installing Guest Operating System</title><link>http://localhost:80/preparing-VPS-templates/installing-guest-operating-system-tr-TR</link><description>&lt;p style="line-height: normal; margin: 0in 0in 0pt;" class="MsoNormal"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: 'Times New Roman','serif'; font-size: 9.5pt;" lang="TR"&gt;&lt;a href="http://www.websitepanel.net/documentation"&gt;&lt;span style="color: windowtext; text-decoration: none; text-underline: none;"&gt;Belgeler&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &amp;gt; &lt;a href="http://www.websitepanel.net/preparing-VPS-templates/index"&gt;&lt;span style="color: windowtext; text-decoration: none; text-underline: none;"&gt;VPS Şablonları Hazırlama&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h1 style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: 'Arial','sans-serif'; font-size: 17pt;" lang="TR"&gt;Misafir İşletim Sistemi Kurma&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p style="line-height: normal; margin-bottom: 0pt;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: 'Arial','sans-serif'; font-size: 9.5pt;" lang="TR"&gt;Yeni oluşturulan ana VM, Windows Server 2008 kurulum DVD'sinden y&amp;uuml;klenir ve OS kurulum işlemi başlar: &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="/Media/WindowsLiveWriter/InstallingGuestOperatingSystem_AE6F/image_2.png"&gt;&lt;img style="display: inline; border: 0px;" title="image" border="0" alt="image" src="/Media/WindowsLiveWriter/InstallingGuestOperatingSystem_AE6F/image_thumb.png" width="404" height="348" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="line-height: normal; margin-bottom: 0pt;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: 'Arial','sans-serif'; font-size: 9.5pt;" lang="TR"&gt;Fare desteği i&amp;ccedil;in T&amp;uuml;mleştirme Hizmetlerinin misafir OS'de kurulması gerektiğinden farenin bu durumda kullanılamayacağını unutmayın. &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="line-height: normal; margin-bottom: 0pt;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: 'Arial','sans-serif'; font-size: 9.5pt;" lang="TR"&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="line-height: normal; margin-bottom: 0pt;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: 'Arial','sans-serif'; font-size: 9.5pt;" lang="TR"&gt;Listeden Windows Server 2008 Edition se&amp;ccedil;in ve &amp;ldquo;İleri&amp;rdquo; d&amp;uuml;ğmesini tıklatın. &amp;Ouml;rneğimizde &amp;ldquo;Windows Server 2008 Standard (Tam Kurulum) x64&amp;rdquo; kurulmaktadır. &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="line-height: normal; margin-bottom: 0pt;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: 'Arial','sans-serif'; font-size: 9.5pt;" lang="TR"&gt;Windows Server 2008 kurmak i&amp;ccedil;in sihirbazdaki diğer adımları uygulayın: &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="/Media/WindowsLiveWriter/InstallingGuestOperatingSystem_AE6F/image_4.png"&gt;&lt;img style="display: inline; border: 0px;" title="image" border="0" alt="image" src="/Media/WindowsLiveWriter/InstallingGuestOperatingSystem_AE6F/image_thumb_1.png" width="404" height="348" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="line-height: normal; margin-bottom: 0pt;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: 'Arial','sans-serif'; font-size: 9.5pt;" lang="TR"&gt;Kurulum sırasında, her yeniden başlatmada VM &amp;ldquo;CD veya DVD'den y&amp;uuml;klemek i&amp;ccedil;in herhangi bir tuşa basın...&amp;rdquo; iletisi verir; mesajı dikkate almayın ve HDD'den y&amp;uuml;klemeye devam edin. &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="line-height: normal; margin-bottom: 0pt;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: 'Arial','sans-serif'; font-size: 9.5pt;" lang="TR"&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="line-height: normal; margin-bottom: 0pt;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: 'Arial','sans-serif'; font-size: 9.5pt;" lang="TR"&gt;Windows Server 2008 kurulum işlemi tamamlandıktan sonra OS, &amp;ldquo;Windows'a Hoş Geldiniz&amp;rdquo; aşamasını y&amp;uuml;kler. Y&amp;ouml;netici hesabı şifresi belirleyin: &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
