&lt;p style="line-height: normal; text-indent: -0.25in; margin: 0in 0in 0pt 0.5in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;" class="MsoNormal"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: Symbol; font-size: 9.5pt; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;" lang="TR"&gt;&lt;span style="mso-list: Ignore;"&gt;&amp;middot;&lt;span style="font: 7pt 'Times New Roman';"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: 'Times New Roman','serif'; font-size: 9.5pt;" lang="TR"&gt;&amp;ldquo;Şifreler karmaşıklık gereksinimlerini karşılamalıdır&amp;rdquo; &amp;ouml;ğesine basın ve Devre Dışı se&amp;ccedil;in. &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="line-height: normal; text-indent: -0.25in; margin: 0in 0in 0pt 0.5in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;" class="MsoNormal"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: Symbol; font-size: 9.5pt; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;" lang="TR"&gt;&lt;span style="mso-list: Ignore;"&gt;&amp;middot;&lt;span style="font: 7pt 'Times New Roman';"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: 'Times New Roman','serif'; font-size: 9.5pt;" lang="TR"&gt;&amp;ldquo;Şifreleri geri d&amp;ouml;n&amp;uuml;şt&amp;uuml;r&amp;uuml;lebilir şifreleme ile sakla&amp;rdquo; &amp;ouml;ğesinde varsayılan Devre Dışı ayarlarını koruyun.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="line-height: normal; text-indent: -0.25in; margin: 0in 0in 0pt 0.5in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;" class="MsoNormal"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: Symbol; font-size: 9.5pt; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;" lang="TR"&gt;&lt;span style="mso-list: Ignore;"&gt;&amp;middot;&lt;span style="font: 7pt 'Times New Roman';"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: 'Times New Roman','serif'; font-size: 9.5pt;" lang="TR"&gt;Tamam &amp;ouml;ğesini tıklatın.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Jul 2011 23:21:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">http://localhost:80/preparing-VPS-templates/set-password-policy-tr-TR</guid></item><item><title>Ana VHD Yedekleme</title><link>http://localhost:80/preparing-VPS-templates/backup-master-vhd-tr-TR</link><description>&lt;p style="line-height: normal; margin-bottom: 0pt;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: 'Arial','sans-serif'; font-size: 9.5pt;" lang="TR"&gt;&lt;a href="http://www.websitepanel.net/documentation"&gt;&lt;span style="color: #000000;" color="#000000"&gt;Belgeler&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &amp;gt; &lt;a href="http://www.websitepanel.net/preparing-VPS-templates/index"&gt;&lt;span style="color: #000000;" color="#000000"&gt;VPS Şablonları Hazırlama&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h1 style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: 'Arial','sans-serif'; font-size: 17pt;" lang="TR"&gt;Ana VHD Yedekleme&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p style="line-height: normal; margin-bottom: 0pt;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: 'Arial','sans-serif'; font-size: 9.5pt;" lang="TR"&gt;Diğer adımlara ge&amp;ccedil;meden &amp;ouml;nce ana VHD'yi yedekleyin: &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="line-height: normal; margin-bottom: 0pt;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: 'Arial','sans-serif'; font-size: 9.5pt;" lang="TR"&gt;1. Sanal bilgisayarı kapatın (&amp;ldquo;G&amp;uuml;c&amp;uuml; kapatmayın&amp;rdquo;!). &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="line-height: normal; margin-bottom: 0pt;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: 'Arial','sans-serif'; font-size: 9.5pt;" lang="TR"&gt;2. .VHD dosyasını bulun ve g&amp;uuml;venli bir konuma kaydedin, &amp;ouml;rneğin &amp;ldquo;M:\VPS\Master\Backups&amp;rdquo; klas&amp;ouml;r&amp;uuml;. VM &amp;ouml;zellikleri iletişim penceresini a&amp;ccedil;arak VHD dosyasının tam konumunu g&amp;ouml;rebilirsiniz: &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="line-height: normal; margin-bottom: 0pt;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: 'Arial','sans-serif'; font-size: 9.5pt;" lang="TR"&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="line-height: normal; margin-bottom: 0pt;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: 'Arial','sans-serif'; font-size: 9.5pt;" lang="TR"&gt;&amp;Ouml;nemli not: Farklı sanal sabit s&amp;uuml;r&amp;uuml;c&amp;uuml;lerin oluşturulmasına neden olduğundan sistem anlık g&amp;ouml;r&amp;uuml;nt&amp;uuml;leri almayın (Hyper-V Anlık G&amp;ouml;r&amp;uuml;nt&amp;uuml; Alma ile ilgili daha fazla bilgi almak i&amp;ccedil;in şu makaleye bakabilirsiniz: &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="line-height: normal; margin-bottom: 0pt;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: 'Arial','sans-serif'; font-size: 9.5pt;" lang="TR"&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="line-height: normal; margin-bottom: 0pt;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: 'Arial','sans-serif'; font-size: 9.5pt;" lang="TR"&gt;&lt;a href="http://blogs.msdn.com/virtual_pc_guy/archive/2008/03/11/virtual-machine-snapshotting-under-hyper-v.aspx"&gt;&lt;span style="color: #000000;" color="#000000"&gt;http://blogs.msdn.com/virtual_pc_guy/archive/2008/03/11/virtual-machine-snapshotting-under-hyper-v.aspx&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;) ve sonu&amp;ccedil; olarak ana şablonlar &amp;ccedil;eşitli par&amp;ccedil;alara ayrılacaktır. &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="line-height: normal; margin-bottom: 0pt;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: 'Arial','sans-serif'; font-size: 9.5pt;" lang="TR"&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="line-height: normal; margin-bottom: 0pt;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: 'Arial','sans-serif'; font-size: 9.5pt;" lang="TR"&gt;VHD yedekleme sonrasında VM'yi yeniden başlatın. &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Jul 2011 23:19:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">http://localhost:80/preparing-VPS-templates/backup-master-vhd-tr-TR</guid></item><item><title>WSP Sanal Bilgisayar Yapılandırma Hizmeti Kurma</title><link>http://localhost:80/preparing-VPS-templates/install-wsp-virtual-machine-configuration-service-tr-TR</link><description>&lt;p style="line-height: normal; margin: 0in 0in 0pt;" class="MsoNormal"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: 'Times New Roman','serif'; color: black; font-size: 9.5pt;" lang="TR"&gt;&lt;a href="http://www.websitepanel.net/documentation"&gt;&lt;span style="color: black; text-decoration: none; text-underline: none;"&gt;Belgeler&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &amp;gt; &lt;a href="http://www.websitepanel.net/preparing-VPS-templates/index"&gt;&lt;span style="color: black; text-decoration: none; text-underline: none;"&gt;VPS Şablonları Hazırlama&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="line-height: normal; margin: 0in 0in 0pt; mso-outline-level: 1;" class="MsoNormal"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: 'Times New Roman','serif'; color: black; font-size: 17pt; mso-font-kerning: 18.0pt;" lang="TR"&gt;WSP Sanal Bilgisayar Yapılandırma Hizmeti Kurma&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="line-height: normal; margin: 0in 0in 0pt;" class="MsoNormal"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: 'Times New Roman','serif'; color: black; font-size: 9.5pt;" lang="TR"&gt;WebsitePanel Sanal Bilgisayar Yapılandırma Hizmeti (WSP VmConfig), misafir işletim sisteminde &amp;ccedil;alışan ve aşağıdaki işlevlere sahip bir Windows Hizmetidir:&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="line-height: normal; text-indent: -0.25in; margin: 0in 0in 0pt 0.25in; mso-list: l3 level1 lfo1;" class="MsoNormal"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: Symbol; color: black; font-size: 9.5pt; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;" lang="TR"&gt;&lt;span style="mso-list: Ignore;"&gt;&amp;middot;&lt;span style="font: 7pt 'Times New Roman';"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: 'Times New Roman','serif'; color: black; font-size: 9.5pt;" lang="TR"&gt;Misafir işletim sisteminin yapılandırılması i&amp;ccedil;in denetim mod&amp;uuml;llerini y&amp;uuml;r&amp;uuml;t&amp;uuml;r.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="line-height: normal; text-indent: -0.25in; margin: 0in 0in 0pt 0.25in; mso-list: l3 level1 lfo1;" class="MsoNormal"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: Symbol; color: black; font-size: 9.5pt; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;" lang="TR"&gt;&lt;span style="mso-list: Ignore;"&gt;&amp;middot;&lt;span style="font: 7pt 'Times New Roman';"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: 'Times New Roman','serif'; color: black; font-size: 9.5pt;" lang="TR"&gt;WebsitePanel kullanıcı arabiriminde (UI) g&amp;ouml;r&amp;uuml;nt&amp;uuml;lenen ger&amp;ccedil;ek zamanlı istatistikler alır (RAM, HDD).&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="line-height: normal; margin: 0in 0in 0pt;" class="MsoNormal"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: 'Times New Roman','serif'; color: black; font-size: 9.5pt;" lang="TR"&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="line-height: normal; margin: 0in 0in 0pt;" class="MsoNormal"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: 'Times New Roman','serif'; color: black; font-size: 9.5pt;" lang="TR"&gt;WSP VmConfig, şu denetim mod&amp;uuml;llerini i&amp;ccedil;erir:&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="line-height: normal; text-indent: -0.25in; margin: 0in 0in 0pt 0.25in; mso-list: l2 level1 lfo2;" class="MsoNormal"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: Symbol; color: black; font-size: 9.5pt; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;" lang="TR"&gt;&lt;span style="mso-list: Ignore;"&gt;&amp;middot;&lt;span style="font: 7pt 'Times New Roman';"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: 'Times New Roman','serif'; color: black; font-size: 9.5pt;" lang="TR"&gt;Bilgisayar adı değiştirme&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="line-height: normal; text-indent: -0.25in; margin: 0in 0in 0pt 0.25in; mso-list: l2 level1 lfo2;" class="MsoNormal"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: Symbol; color: black; font-size: 9.5pt; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;" lang="TR"&gt;&lt;span style="mso-list: Ignore;"&gt;&amp;middot;&lt;span style="font: 7pt 'Times New Roman';"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: 'Times New Roman','serif'; color: black; font-size: 9.5pt;" lang="TR"&gt;Y&amp;ouml;netici şifresi değiştirme&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="line-height: normal; text-indent: -0.25in; margin: 0in 0in 0pt 0.25in; mso-list: l2 level1 lfo2;" class="MsoNormal"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: Symbol; color: black; font-size: 9.5pt; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;" lang="TR"&gt;&lt;span style="mso-list: Ignore;"&gt;&amp;middot;&lt;span style="font: 7pt 'Times New Roman';"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: 'Times New Roman','serif'; color: black; font-size: 9.5pt;" lang="TR"&gt;Ağ adapt&amp;ouml;r&amp;uuml; yapılandırması değiştirme&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="line-height: normal; margin: 0in 0in 0pt;" class="MsoNormal"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: 'Times New Roman','serif'; color: black; font-size: 9.5pt;" lang="TR"&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="line-height: normal; margin: 0in 0in 0pt;" class="MsoNormal"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: 'Times New Roman','serif'; color: black; font-size: 9.5pt;" lang="TR"&gt;WSP VmConfig hizmeti, &amp;ldquo;Hyper-V Data Exchange&amp;rdquo; t&amp;uuml;mleştirme bileşeni aracılığıyla Hyper-V ana bilgisayarı ile iletişim kurar; bu nedenle hizmetin &amp;ccedil;alışır durumda olduğundan emin olun.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="line-height: normal; margin: 0in 0in 0pt;" class="MsoNormal"&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: 'Times New Roman','serif'; color: black; font-size: 9.5pt;" lang="TR"&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="line-height: normal; margin: 0in 0in 0pt;" class="MsoNormal"&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: 'Times New Roman','serif'; color: black; font-size: 9.5pt;" lang="TR"&gt;Sistem gereksinimleri:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: 'Times New Roman','serif'; color: black; font-size: 9.5pt;" lang="TR"&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
