&lt;p style="line-height: normal; margin-bottom: 0pt;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: 'Arial','sans-serif'; font-size: 9.5pt;" lang="TR"&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Jul 2011 23:15:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">http://localhost:80/preparing-VPS-templates/generalize-master-image-tr-TR</guid></item><item><title>VPS Şablonunu Kitaplığa Uygulama</title><link>http://localhost:80/preparing-VPS-templates/deploying-vps-template-to-library-tr-TR</link><description>&lt;p style="line-height: normal; margin-bottom: 0pt;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: 'Arial','sans-serif'; font-size: 9.5pt;" lang="TR"&gt;&lt;a href="http://www.websitepanel.net/documentation"&gt;&lt;span style="color: #000000;" color="#000000"&gt;Belgeler&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &amp;gt; &lt;a href="http://www.websitepanel.net/preparing-VPS-templates/index"&gt;&lt;span style="color: #000000;" color="#000000"&gt;VPS Şablonları Hazırlama&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="line-height: normal; margin: 0in 0in 0pt; mso-outline-level: 1;" class="MsoNormal"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: 'Times New Roman','serif'; font-size: 17pt; mso-font-kerning: 18.0pt;" lang="TR"&gt;VPS Şablonunu Kitaplığa Uygulama&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="line-height: normal; margin: 0in 0in 0pt;" class="MsoNormal"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: 'Times New Roman','serif'; font-size: 9.5pt;" lang="TR"&gt;Ana VHD dosyasını orijinal konumundan (&amp;ouml;rneğimizde &amp;ldquo;M:\VPS\Master\Master - Windows 2008 Standard x64&amp;rdquo;) WSP VPS &amp;ccedil;&amp;ouml;z&amp;uuml;m&amp;uuml; &amp;ldquo;Şablonlar&amp;rdquo; klas&amp;ouml;r&amp;uuml;ne (&amp;ouml;rneğimizde C:\VPS\Templates&amp;rdquo;) kopyalayın ve adını &amp;ldquo;Windows 2008 Standard x64.vhd&amp;rdquo; olarak değiştirin.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="line-height: normal; text-indent: -0.25in; margin: 0in 0in 0pt 0.25in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;" class="MsoNormal"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: Symbol; font-size: 9.5pt; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;" lang="TR"&gt;&lt;span style="mso-list: Ignore;"&gt;&amp;middot;&lt;span style="font: 7pt 'Times New Roman';"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: 'Times New Roman','serif'; font-size: 9.5pt;" lang="TR"&gt;&lt;a href="http://www.websitepanel.net/preparing-VPS-templates/replace-answer-file-with-template"&gt;&lt;span style="color: #000000;" color="#000000"&gt;Yanıt Dosyasını Şablonla Değiştirme &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="line-height: normal; text-indent: -0.25in; margin: 0in 0in 0pt 0.25in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;" class="MsoNormal"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: Symbol; font-size: 9.5pt; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;" lang="TR"&gt;&lt;span style="mso-list: Ignore;"&gt;&amp;middot;&lt;span style="font: 7pt 'Times New Roman';"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: 'Times New Roman','serif'; font-size: 9.5pt;" lang="TR"&gt;&lt;a href="http://www.websitepanel.net/preparing-VPS-templates/create-templates-index-file"&gt;&lt;span style="color: #000000;" color="#000000"&gt;Şablonlar Dizin Dosyası Oluşturma&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="line-height: normal; margin-bottom: 0pt;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: 'Arial','sans-serif'; font-size: 9.5pt;" lang="TR"&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Jul 2011 23:07:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">http://localhost:80/preparing-VPS-templates/deploying-vps-template-to-library-tr-TR</guid></item><item><title>Yanıt Dosyasını Şablonla Değiştirme</title><link>http://localhost:80/preparing-VPS-templates/replace-answer-file-with-template-tr-TR</link><description>&lt;p style="line-height: normal; margin: 0in 0in 0pt;" class="MsoNormal"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: 'Times New Roman','serif'; font-size: 9.5pt;" lang="TR"&gt;&lt;a href="http://www.websitepanel.net/documentation"&gt;&lt;span style="color: #000000;" color="#000000"&gt;Belgeler&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &amp;gt; &lt;a href="http://www.websitepanel.net/preparing-VPS-templates/index"&gt;&lt;span style="color: #000000;" color="#000000"&gt;VPS Şablonları Hazırlama&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h1 style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: 'Arial','sans-serif'; font-size: 17pt;" lang="TR"&gt;Yanıt Dosyasını Şablonla Değiştirme&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p style="line-height: normal; margin-bottom: 0pt;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: 'Arial','sans-serif'; font-size: 9.5pt;" lang="TR"&gt;Buradan [bağlantı sağlanacak] ulaşabileceğiniz &amp;ldquo;vmutils&amp;rdquo; aracını kullanarak kopyalanan VHD'yi bağlayın: &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="line-height: normal; margin-bottom: 0pt;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: 'Arial','sans-serif'; font-size: 9.5pt;" lang="TR"&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;pre style="line-height: normal; margin: 0in 0in 0pt;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 9.5pt;" lang="TR"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: Lucida Console;" face="Lucida Console"&gt;vmutils MountVHD &amp;ndash;yol &amp;ldquo;c:\VPS\Templates\Windows 2008 Standard x64.vhd&amp;rdquo;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;pre style="line-height: normal; margin: 0in 0in 0pt;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 9.5pt;" lang="TR"&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: Lucida Console;" face="Lucida Console"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;p style="line-height: normal; margin-bottom: 0pt;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: 'Arial','sans-serif'; font-size: 9.5pt;" lang="TR"&gt;&amp;ldquo;Bilgisayar Y&amp;ouml;netimi&amp;rdquo; eklentisini a&amp;ccedil;ın ve &amp;ldquo;Disk Y&amp;ouml;netimi&amp;rdquo; d&amp;uuml;ğ&amp;uuml;m&amp;uuml;n&amp;uuml; genişletin. Bağlanan diski &amp;ccedil;evrimi&amp;ccedil;i hale getirin (&amp;ccedil;evrimdışı ise): &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="line-height: normal; margin-bottom: 0pt;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: 'Arial','sans-serif'; font-size: 9.5pt;" lang="TR"&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="line-height: normal; margin-bottom: 0pt;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: 'Arial','sans-serif'; font-size: 9.5pt;" lang="TR"&gt;Alternatif olarak, diski &amp;ccedil;evrimi&amp;ccedil;i hale getirebilir ve DiskPart yardımcı programını kullanarak birim &amp;ldquo;readonly&amp;rdquo; &amp;ouml;zniteliğini (ayarlanmışsa) silebilirsiniz: &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="line-height: normal; margin-bottom: 0pt;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: 'Arial','sans-serif'; font-size: 9.5pt;" lang="TR"&gt;Komut satırında: &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;pre style="line-height: normal; margin: 0in 0in 0pt;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 9.5pt;" lang="TR"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: Lucida Console;" face="Lucida Console"&gt;C&amp;gt; DiskPart&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;p style="line-height: normal; margin-bottom: 0pt;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: 'Arial','sans-serif'; font-size: 9.5pt;" lang="TR"&gt;T&amp;uuml;m kullanılabilir diskleri g&amp;ouml;r&amp;uuml;nt&amp;uuml;leyin: &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;pre style="line-height: normal; margin: 0in 0in 0pt;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 9.5pt;" lang="TR"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: Lucida Console;" face="Lucida Console"&gt;list disk&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;p style="line-height: normal; margin-bottom: 0pt;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: 'Arial','sans-serif'; font-size: 9.5pt;" lang="TR"&gt;Dizinini belirleyerek ilgili diski se&amp;ccedil;in: &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;pre style="line-height: normal; margin: 0in 0in 0pt;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 9.5pt;" lang="TR"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: Lucida Console;" face="Lucida Console"&gt;select disk=&amp;lt;N&amp;gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;p style="line-height: normal; margin-bottom: 0pt;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: 'Arial','sans-serif'; font-size: 9.5pt;" lang="TR"&gt;Se&amp;ccedil;ilen diski &amp;ccedil;evrimi&amp;ccedil;i hale getirin: &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;pre style="line-height: normal; margin: 0in 0in 0pt;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 9.5pt;" lang="TR"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: Lucida Console;" face="Lucida Console"&gt;online disk noerr&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;p style="line-height: normal; margin-bottom: 0pt;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: 'Arial','sans-serif'; font-size: 9.5pt;" lang="TR"&gt;T&amp;uuml;m birimleri listeleyin: &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;pre style="line-height: normal; margin: 0in 0in 0pt;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 9.5pt;" lang="TR"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: Lucida Console;" face="Lucida Console"&gt;list volume&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;p style="line-height: normal; margin-bottom: 0pt;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: 'Arial','sans-serif'; font-size: 9.5pt;" lang="TR"&gt;Dizinini veya s&amp;uuml;r&amp;uuml;c&amp;uuml; harfini belirleyerek birimi se&amp;ccedil;in: &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;pre style="line-height: normal; margin: 0in 0in 0pt;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 9.5pt;" lang="TR"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: Lucida Console;" face="Lucida Console"&gt;select volume=&amp;lt;N&amp;gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;p style="line-height: normal; margin-bottom: 0pt;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: 'Arial','sans-serif'; font-size: 9.5pt;" lang="TR"&gt;readonly işaretini silin: &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;pre style="line-height: normal; margin: 0in 0in 0pt;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 9.5pt;" lang="TR"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: Lucida Console;" face="Lucida Console"&gt;attributes volume clear &lt;span class="kwrd"&gt;readonly&lt;/span&gt; noerr&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;p style="line-height: normal; margin-bottom: 0pt;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: 'Arial','sans-serif'; font-size: 9.5pt;" lang="TR"&gt;DiskPart uygulamasından &amp;ccedil;ıkın: &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;pre style="line-height: normal; margin: 0in 0in 0pt;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 9.5pt;" lang="TR"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: Lucida Console;" face="Lucida Console"&gt;exit&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;p style="line-height: normal; margin-bottom: 0pt;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: 'Arial','sans-serif'; font-size: 9.5pt;" lang="TR"&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="line-height: normal; margin-bottom: 0pt;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: 'Arial','sans-serif'; font-size: 9.5pt;" lang="TR"&gt;Windows Explorer uygulamasında, bağlı diskteki &amp;ldquo;Windows\System32\sysprep&amp;rdquo; klas&amp;ouml;r&amp;uuml;n&amp;uuml; a&amp;ccedil;ın. &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="line-height: normal; margin-bottom: 0pt;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: 'Arial','sans-serif'; font-size: 9.5pt;" lang="TR"&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="line-height: normal; margin-bottom: 0pt;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: 'Arial','sans-serif'; font-size: 9.5pt;" lang="TR"&gt;&amp;ldquo;Windows Server 2008 i&amp;ccedil;in Sysprep Dosyalarını&amp;rdquo; buradan [bağlantı sağlanacak] y&amp;uuml;kleyin ve bir klas&amp;ouml;re &amp;ccedil;ıkarın. &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="line-height: normal; margin-bottom: 0pt;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: 'Arial','sans-serif'; font-size: 9.5pt;" lang="TR"&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="line-height: normal; margin-bottom: 0pt;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: 'Arial','sans-serif'; font-size: 9.5pt;" lang="TR"&gt;Bağlı diskin &amp;ldquo;Windows\System32\sysprep&amp;rdquo; klas&amp;ouml;r&amp;uuml;ndeki &amp;ldquo;unattend.xml&amp;rdquo; dosyasının i&amp;ccedil;eriğini arşivden &amp;ldquo;unattend-template.xml&amp;rdquo; ile değiştirin. &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="line-height: normal; margin-bottom: 0pt;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: 'Arial','sans-serif'; font-size: 9.5pt;" lang="TR"&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="line-height: normal; margin-bottom: 0pt;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: 'Arial','sans-serif'; font-size: 9.5pt;" lang="TR"&gt;Sağlanan şablonu kendi şablonunuz i&amp;ccedil;in başlangı&amp;ccedil; noktası olarak kullanabilir ve kendi barındırma kurumunuza &amp;ouml;zel ilave ayarlar ekleyebilirsiniz. Şablonu WSIM ile d&amp;uuml;zenlemeyin, şablon talimatlarında ge&amp;ccedil;erli XML i&amp;ccedil;indedir ve WSIM tarafından y&amp;uuml;klenmez. Not Defteri uygulamasını veya başka bir metin d&amp;uuml;zenleyiciyi kullanın. Kullanılabilir şablon değişkenlerinin listesini &lt;a href="http://www.websitepanel.net/hyper-v-module/index"&gt;&lt;span style="color: #000000;" color="#000000"&gt;WebsitePanel Hyper-V Mod&amp;uuml;l&amp;uuml; Kurulum Kılavuzunda bulabilirsiniz&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;. &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="line-height: normal; margin-bottom: 0pt;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: 'Arial','sans-serif'; font-size: 9.5pt;" lang="TR"&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="line-height: normal; margin-bottom: 0pt;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: 'Arial','sans-serif'; font-size: 9.5pt;" lang="TR"&gt;L&amp;uuml;tfen sağlanan şablonda &amp;ldquo;ProductKey&amp;rdquo; &amp;ouml;ğesinin bulunmadığına dikkat edin; Windows Ayarları &amp;ldquo;&amp;ouml;zelleştir&amp;rdquo; ge&amp;ccedil;işi sırasında &amp;ldquo;&amp;Uuml;r&amp;uuml;n anahtarı gir&amp;rdquo; iletişim penceresini ge&amp;ccedil;mek i&amp;ccedil;in eklemeniz gerekecektir. &amp;ldquo;ProductKey&amp;rdquo; &amp;ouml;ğesi &amp;ldquo;&lt;i&gt;Microsoft-Windows-Shell-Setup&lt;/i&gt;&amp;rdquo; bileşenine eklenmelidir, &amp;ouml;rneğin: &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;pre style="line-height: normal; margin: 0in 0in 0pt;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 9.5pt;" lang="TR"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: Lucida Console;" face="Lucida Console"&gt;&amp;lt;component name=&lt;span class="str"&gt;"Microsoft-Windows-Shell-Setup"&lt;/span&gt; ...&amp;gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
