&lt;p style="line-height: normal; margin: 0in 0in 0pt; background: white; tab-stops: 45.8pt 91.6pt 137.4pt 183.2pt 229.0pt 274.8pt 320.6pt 366.4pt 412.2pt 458.0pt 503.8pt 549.6pt 595.4pt 641.2pt 687.0pt 732.8pt;" class="MsoNormal"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: 'Times New Roman','serif'; font-size: 12pt;" lang="TR"&gt;&amp;lt;/items&amp;gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="line-height: normal; margin: 0in 0in 0pt;" class="MsoNormal"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: 'Times New Roman','serif'; font-size: 9.5pt;" lang="TR"&gt;index.xml dosyası oluşturulurken şunlara dikkat edin: &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul style="margin-top: 0in;" type="disc"&gt;
&lt;li style="line-height: normal; margin: 0in 0in 0pt; tab-stops: list .5in; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo2;" class="MsoNormal"&gt;&lt;i&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: 'Times New Roman','serif'; font-size: 9.5pt;" lang="TR"&gt;Dosya uzantısı&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: 'Times New Roman','serif'; font-size: 9.5pt;" lang="TR"&gt; &amp;ldquo;.xml&amp;rdquo; olmalıdır. Windows uygulamasında yeni bir .txt dosyası oluşturulurken bilinen uzantı gizlenebilir, bu nedenle yanlış anlama s&amp;ouml;z konusu olabilir. &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style="line-height: normal; margin: 0in 0in 0pt; tab-stops: list .5in; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo2;" class="MsoNormal"&gt;&lt;i&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: 'Times New Roman','serif'; font-size: 9.5pt;" lang="TR"&gt;Dosya kodlama&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: 'Times New Roman','serif'; font-size: 9.5pt;" lang="TR"&gt;. Şablon adları ve a&amp;ccedil;ıklamalarında &amp;ccedil;eşitli ulusal karakterlerin kullanılabilmesi i&amp;ccedil;in UTF-8 tavsiye edilir. Kodlamayı, Not Defteri uygulaması &amp;ldquo;Farklı kaydet...&amp;rdquo; iletişim penceresinde se&amp;ccedil;ebilirsiniz.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;pre style="line-height: normal; margin: 0in 0in 0pt; background: white;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: Consolas;" lang="TR"&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: small;" size="3"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Jul 2011 23:06:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">http://localhost:80/preparing-VPS-templates/create-templates-index-file-tr-TR</guid></item><item><title>VPS Misafir OS Denetimi</title><link>http://localhost:80/preparing-VPS-templates/vps-guest-os-provisioning-tr-TR</link><description>&lt;p style="line-height: normal; margin-bottom: 0pt;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: 'Arial','sans-serif'; font-size: 9.5pt;" lang="TR"&gt;&lt;a href="http://www.websitepanel.net/documentation"&gt;&lt;span style="color: #000000;" color="#000000"&gt;Belgeler&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &amp;gt; &lt;a href="http://www.websitepanel.net/preparing-VPS-templates/index"&gt;&lt;span style="color: #000000;" color="#000000"&gt;VPS Şablonları Hazırlama&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="line-height: normal; margin: 0in 0in 0pt; mso-outline-level: 1;" class="MsoNormal"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: 'Times New Roman','serif'; font-size: 17pt; mso-font-kerning: 18.0pt;" lang="TR"&gt;VPS Misafir OS Denetimi&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="line-height: normal; margin: 0in 0in 0pt;" class="MsoNormal"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: 'Times New Roman','serif'; font-size: 9.5pt;" lang="TR"&gt;Aşağıdaki şemada VPS misafir OS denetimi &amp;ouml;zetlenmekte ve WSP yeni bir VPS oluşturduğunda neler olduğu daha net bir şekilde anlatılmaktadır: &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="line-height: normal; margin: 0in 0in 0pt;" class="MsoNormal"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: 'Times New Roman','serif'; font-size: 9.5pt;" lang="TR"&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
